snippet.title: Amber Heard Gets Forced To Apologize To Johnny Depp By Her Lawyer!
snippet.description:
🖤 Amber Heard Gets Forced To Apologize To Johnny Depp By Her Lawyer!
Amber Heard’s legal team has apologised to Johnny Depp and issued a retraction of a statement they made after the estranged couple reached their divorce settlement. Heard, 30, dismissed her petition for a restraining order against Depp, 50, on Tuesday. The pair reached an out of court settlement of a reported £5.4 million.
